#

Pork Meat Gravy with Herb Infusion

$15.99
350 kcal

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

Comfort FoodHeartyMain Dish

Description

A rich and hearty pork meat gravy infused with fresh herbs, perfect for enhancing your favorite dishes.

Ingredients

  • Pork shoulder: 2 lbs
  • Onion: 1 large, diced
  • Carrots: 2, diced
  • Celery: 2 stalks, diced
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Chicken broth: 4 cups
  • Fresh thyme: 2 sprigs
  • Fresh rosemary: 2 sprigs
  • Bay leaves: 2
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Cornstarch: 2 tbsp (optional, for thickening)
